- Ge'ez text + translation. Cross-check with 4QEnoch Aramaic fragments (4Q201-202) where available — Aramaic + translation.
- CRITICAL: Is the word-play on Hermon/ḥerem (ban/curse) present in the Aramaic fragments or only in the Ge'ez?

